page_content: Discusses an unaccompanied luggage transfer service for bikers and hikers in Graubünden.

Discusses the replacement of the EDV-Bibliothekssystem Dobis/Libis in the Bündner Kantonsbibliothek due to end of support.
Discusses the need for gender-neutral language in tax forms.

Discusses an art installation by frölicher | bietenhader that explores the instability of technology.
Announces the appointment of Fernando Guntern as the new head of the Personnel Office in Graubünden, who has a background in software development.
